{"tid":153572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖四年，點繼續好","createTime":"2017-03-12T16:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T17:55:36.000Z","uid":90815,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8514887f0cc93b90ca455c328239775a091020e7","tid":153572,"uid":90815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:22:10.000Z","msg":"同男朋友拍拖拍左四年幾喇<br />\n計識就識左好多喇 十年都有<br />\n而家開始 都好平淡喇 平平淡淡都好既<br />\n但過於平淡 已經開始好悶 好無聊<br />\n每樣野都一樣 都係食飯 睇戲 做<br />\n次序 程序都一樣 無變 無激情 無浪漫<br />\n佢都吾係啲識浪漫既人 吾識哄我 <br />\n我尼頭諗佢成日都吾哄下我 <br />\n就諗其實佢係咪都開始吾鍾意我 <br />\n一齊都只係因應習慣了<br />\n我都好掛住一開始拍拖果半年 <br />\n大家都放大家係第一 諗點樣令對方開心<br />\n有冇啲拍左咁耐又成功既人分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9279a57d25c9b880888a383e92ad579ec2041063","tid":153572,"uid":65911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"40f847988b0a3773841a7189ae13b5c0a55a1c7f","tid":153572,"uid":2193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"尼你老母<br />\n吾你老母"},{"pid":"e2a4d6e43a6fcaf12c87efe4dcb149249c9848ec","tid":153572,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"尼你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb3106918d4803bc61abc9dc5220ceb1f6c8c54","tid":153572,"uid":23853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:25:00.000Z","msg":"平淡是福呀 記住唔好後悔 好既野錯過左就無"},{"pid":"4bc9b4bdc774e66e10d236a1ead0086b0f01ece8","tid":153572,"uid":44724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"需求唔同，不過平淡是福，日後可能會搵到當中樂趣。"},{"pid":"13494bcbbc7c10a1b8fd066b12a9cfb18c9874ae","tid":153572,"uid":62045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"平淡好過轟烈呀。"},{"pid":"adabe20ca94ce0eaf0f30d1dd6c41c54840eca0f","tid":153572,"uid":1732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"不如你主動搵啲樂趣 倒如一齊做啲極限少少既嘢"},{"pid":"d9dca5f8fa52237ce62ee254fc97ae46d2a396e7","tid":153572,"uid":90815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如你主動搵啲樂趣 倒如一齊做啲極限少少既嘢</blockquote><br />\n極限姐係點"},{"pid":"0e089bd1b4475248207bdfce3e4bb2d73ce8cee4","tid":153572,"uid":87781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平淡是福呀 記住唔好後悔 好既野錯過左就無</blockquote><br />\n係囉，珍惜下啦"},{"pid":"05b99e933fe35a6a77ada3bb2af07774d875823d","tid":153572,"uid":90815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"我明平淡好既 但有時我想要少少浪漫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2713fbbeaa98d138a22cf35e82bbe198f4d163","tid":153572,"uid":90815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"而家相處就好似朋友咁 無乜特別"},{"pid":"4f758d612bc0755aaaa176980984524c37803f26","tid":153572,"uid":61060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"pm我，我比d浪漫你"},{"pid":"612130c4d91532cafbb86f8a963ece5baa8eb144","tid":153572,"uid":83226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"教佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8424b62e355db17543ff179d0db6e6f20b9f63","tid":153572,"uid":67778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"扑野/埋單生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64954159ff93730359921350eef178f0d119d671","tid":153572,"uid":44724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明平淡好既 但有時我想要少少浪漫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實一齊睇下片，煮下飯，係眾人眼中已經好浪漫，再唔係咪計劃去旅行，不過我覺得樓主係想要激情。"},{"pid":"fc94beb2464ab6a93b2cbe7543ba6e3ff288dd50","tid":153572,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"我同老婆拍拖9年...結婚1年...應該夠資格過小小料比你...<br />\n<br />\n1.無聊係好正常既事...你唔好下下要個男人製造浪漫比你...其實你都可以做...<br />\n2.每次都係做果D野...無新意...係因為你地無目標...我建議妳同你男朋友可以計劃下旅行之類...<br />\n3.平時性生活多小小情趣...次次個男人比新意你...比比下都想比第二個啦...情趣用品店幫到你<br />\n4.如果我係你條仔。我實飛左你"},{"pid":"74aa469eeb99f9e4784dffbf9ccc5430227b18dc","tid":153572,"uid":24802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"試下融入多d佢既興趣？ 諗下會唔會有時自己有d咩可以再做好d 有咩做左佢會好開心但係你冇做到？ <br />\n咁樣同佢多d話題 佢又會中意你多d錫你多d<br />\n<br />\nbtw平淡係最幸福既事 當你經過過唔開心先發覺原來自己有好多野可以做得更好 原來平淡係咁幸福既時候 你已經返唔到轉頭 愛要及時"},{"pid":"bdbce743892309935fa39c25e0178576ee8cb3e0","tid":153572,"uid":24802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明平淡好既 但有時我想要少少浪漫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時唔一定佢做主動架ma <br />\n你都可以主動做d野"},{"pid":"d40c26ab6671381fb7d77d6245742e38970bbf64","tid":153572,"uid":82140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:55:38.000Z","msg":"去旅行<br />\n由一齊計劃到去完個旅行<br />\n感情應該會好好多<br />\n但行程記住唔好太 Chur"},{"pid":"768a7e653b323db5db0eac337bd8d8057f09c3d7","tid":153572,"uid":71678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T01:03:34.000Z","msg":"咁多5p字先得一個人屌   果然連登充斥住mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3eacbaf3674081ceaf5e76740f75d1998f0875","tid":153572,"uid":4531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T01:42:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c53e70359214e3178e36074bc626137ca0078067","tid":153572,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:25:20.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下點解識左6年先一齊？ btw 平時留意下d有趣野搵佢一齊做啦 再唔係去個旅行"},{"pid":"b3eb318bc6b77be7726d863731e5a98411d926c0","tid":153572,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同老婆拍拖9年...結婚1年...應該夠資格過小小料比你...<br />\n<br />\n1.無聊係好正常既事...你唔好下下要個男人製造浪漫比你...其實你都可以做...<br />\n2.每次都係做果D野...無新意...係因為你地無目標...我建議妳同你男朋友可以計劃下旅行之類...<br />\n3.平時性生活多小小情趣...次次個男人比新意你...比比下都想比第二個啦...情趣用品店幫到你<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4.如果我係你條仔。我實飛左你</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c0cdce1f508d05e7dbf1811f0f1c2f8db2bb7e","tid":153572,"uid":43155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明平淡好既 但有時我想要少少浪漫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n穩定咪算 又要重新識人 又要等人追 除非佢/你無諗繼續行落去"}]}